---

<section class="relative w-full h-[80svh] md:h-[85svh] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/hero.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-black/30 to-black/10"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-light tracking-tighter text-white mb-8 leading-[1.05]">
      Claridad mental.<br/>
      <span class="font-semibold">Rendimiento absoluto.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/70 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
      Combino evidencia científica, tecnología de punta y herramientas prácticas para ayudarte a alcanzar tu máximo potencial — en el deporte, en tu carrera y en tu vida.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
      <a href="#agendar" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium bg-white text-black rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <span class="relative z-10">Agendar Hora</span>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-200 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out"></div>
      </a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium bg-white text-black rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <span class="relative z-10">Ver Servicios</span>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-200 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out"></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
